name: Wabori_Yarou
description:
This is a model for Japanese style tattoos, using trigger words "tatoo" and "wabori".

This tattoo design is a mix of traditional Japanese and Western styles, and the facial patterns may be limited.

This is a model where even with fewer fingers, it doesn't bother you.
